  <h4><a name="help1" id="help1"></a>How do I use Funfooding.com?</h4>
  <p>Sign up and enter your address or zipcode and we'll show you all the places to eat near you. You can then place your order online or by phone.</p>
  
  <h4><a name="help2" id="help2"></a>How do I order online?</h4>
  <p>Choose from our network of providers that take online orders and select the items you'd like to order with a click. It will be added to your food cart. Once you are done selecting the items, click on "check out" and follow the instructions from there.</p>
  
  <h4><a name="help3" id="help3"></a>Where is my food?</h4>
  <p>Check the status of your current order here.</p>
  
  <h4><a name="help4" id="help4"></a>Can I change my order after I place it?</h4>
  <p>Maybe. If you placed your order in the last five minutes, you can click here to submit a change request. Call the provided contact number first to make sure they have not started working on your order.</p>
  
  <h4><a name="help5" id="help5"></a>Did my order go through?</h4>
  <p>Check the status of your current order here.</p>
  
  <h4><a name="help6" id="help6"></a>Does it cost anything extra?</h4>
  <p>Nope. It is free to use our website to place phone and online orders. We don't add any fees to the buyer.</p>
  
  <h4><a name="help7" id="help7"></a>Can I order catering through Funfooding?</h4>
  <p>You sure can. Its like ordering any meal from a seller for a future date and time.
